commentTextItems.html: Pulled it over mid wicket and that's the end of that. West Indies have won by 6 wickets.

commentPostTextItems.html: We are getting ready for the presentation. Sarwan is man of the match, for his knock of 49. After some early jitters for the Windies, the skipper and the dbutante took them home.  That is all for today, do join us on Friday for Canada v West Indies
6 to win 7 for Sarwan to get to his 50

commentTextItems.html: punched to mid off for a single

commentPostTextItems.html: Trott on from the city end
